headline: Chris Stapleton, Jelly Roll and Shaboozey Headline EA SPORTS™ Presents Madden Bowl at Super Bowl LIX
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., January 09, 2025--Electronic Arts Inc. (NASDAQ: EA)- EA SPORTS™ will electrify Friday night of Super Bowl LIX week in New Orleans when EA SPORTS™ Presents Madden Bowl takes over the legendary Orpheum Theater. Headlined by 10x GRAMMY winner Chris Stapleton and 4x GRAMMY Nominee Jelly Roll, with a one of a kind set by 6x GRAMMY nominee and Billboard Hot 100 sensation Shaboozey, the event will also introduce one of the biggest rising stars in country radio, Tucker Wetmore. EA
